def gcd(x, y):
 while y:
  x, y = y, x % y
 return x

def lcm(x, y):
 return (x*y)//(gcd(x,y))

def isPrime(n) : 
 if (n <= 1) : 
  return False
 if (n <= 3) : 
  return True
 if (n % 2 == 0 or n % 3 == 0) : 
  return False
 i = 5
 while(i * i <= n) : 
  if (n % i == 0 or n % (i + 2) == 0) : 
   return False
  i = i + 6
 return True
